## Setup

Require `youtube-dl` as a dependency. Used to get the content metadata. The
easiest is to install it globally using pythons's `pip`.

`sudo pip install youtube-dl`

Alternative installation methods of youtube-dl can be found in the youtube-dl
documentation
https://github.com/rg3/youtube-dl/blob/master/README.md#installation

To get youtoot working you can do several things.
